text: Rosemary Sparrow (born 6 July 1925) was a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
